---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="空き家">
<style is:global>
.page-header { max-width: var(--wide); margin: 0 auto; padding: 4rem 1.25rem 3rem; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); }
.page-eyebrow { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.18em; color: var(--ink-faint); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.page-title { font-size: clamp(28px,4vw,44px); font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); letter-spacing: 0.06em; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
.page-desc { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--ink-light); line-height: 1.9; max-width: 560px; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
.page-count { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-faint); letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
.property-list { max-width: var(--wide); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 0 6rem; }
.property-card { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 380px 1fr; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.2s; }
.property-card:hover { background: var(--paper-mid); }
.property-card:hover .prop-img img { transform: scale(1.03); }
.prop-img { overflow: hidden; background: var(--paper-dark); aspect-ratio: 4/3; }
.prop-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1); }
.prop-body { padding: 2rem 2rem 2rem 2.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; border-left: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); }
.prop-tags { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.prop-tag { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1em; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 2px; }
.prop-tag-area { background: var(--paper-mid); color: var(--ink-light); border: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); }
.prop-tag-type { background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); }
.prop-title { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.5; letter-spacing: 0.04em; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.prop-story { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--ink-light); line-height: 1.85; letter-spacing: 0.02em; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 3; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; overflow: hidden; }
.prop-specs { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 0; margin-top: auto; border-top: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); padding-top: 1.25rem; }
.prop-spec { padding-right: 1.25rem; }
.prop-spec + .prop-spec { padding-left: 1.25rem; border-left: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); }
.prop-spec-label { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--ink-faint); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.prop-spec-value { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink-mid); }
.prop-spec-sub { font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-faint); margin-top: 1px; }
.prop-footer { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; margin-top: 1rem; }
.prop-read-more { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--ink-faint); border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); padding-bottom: 2px; width: fit-content; transition: color 0.2s; }
.property-card:hover .prop-read-more { color: var(--ink); border-color: var(--ink-light); }
@media (max-width: 600px) { .page-header { padding: 2.5rem 1.25rem 2rem; } }
@media (max-width: 760px) {
  .property-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .prop-img { aspect-ratio: 16/9; }
  .prop-body { padding: 1.25rem; border-left: none; border-top: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); }
  .prop-specs { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); gap: 1rem 0; }
  .prop-spec + .prop-spec { border-left: none; padding-left: 0; }
  .prop-spec:nth-child(2) { border-left: 0.5px solid var(--paper-dark); padding-left: 1.25rem; }
}
</style>

<div class="page-header">
  <div class="page-eyebrow">Properties</div>
  <h1 class="page-title">空き家</h1>
  <p class="page-desc">新建材で組み上げられた家ではなく、時間をかけて育てられた家がある。UNDERCURRENTの目線で選んだ、残す価値のある空き家を紹介する。</p>
  <div class="page-count">4 properties</div>
</div>

<div class="property-list">
  <a href="#" class="property-card fade-in">
    <div class="prop-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512917774080-9991f1c4c750?w=800&q=70" alt=""></div>
    <div class="prop-body">
      <div class="prop-title">製材所の隣に建つ、<br>明治期の庄屋屋敷</div>
      <div class="prop-story">岐阜県郡上市、長良川の支流沿いに建つ庄屋屋敷。明治30年代の建築で、地元産ヒノキをふんだんに使った梁と柱が今も健在だ。</div>
      <div class="prop-specs">
        <div class="prop-spec"><div class="prop-spec-label">価格</div><div class="prop-spec-value">580万円</div><div class="prop-spec-sub">要リノベーション</div></div>
        <div class="prop-spec"><div class="prop-spec-label">延床面積</div><div class="prop-spec-value">248㎡</div><div class="prop-spec-sub">母屋のみ</div></div>
        <div class="prop-spec"><div class="prop-spec-label">築年数</div><div class="prop-spec-value">築約120年</div><div class="prop-spec-sub">明治30年代</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="prop-footer">
        <div class="prop-tags"><span class="prop-tag prop-tag-area">岐阜県</span><span class="prop-tag prop-tag-type">古民家</span></div>
        <span class="prop-read-more">詳しく見る</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </a>
  <a href="#" class="property-card fade-in">
    <div class="prop-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?w=800&q=70" alt=""></div>
    <div class="prop-body">
      <div class="prop-title">諏訪湖を望む丘に建つ、<br>大正期の木造住宅</div>
      <div class="prop-story">長野県諏訪市の高台に建つ大正期の木造2階建て。諏訪湖を一望できる立地で、当時の建築家による設計が随所に見られる。</div>
      <div class="prop-specs">
        <div class="prop-spec"><div class="prop-spec-label">価格</div><div class="prop-spec-value">320万円</div><div class="prop-spec-sub">現状渡し</div></div>
        <div class="prop-spec"><div class="prop-spec-label">延床面積</div><div class="prop-spec-value">132㎡</div><div class="prop-spec-sub">2階建て</div></div>
        <div class="prop-spec"><div class="prop-spec-label">築年数</div><div class="prop-spec-value">築約100年</div><div class="prop-spec-sub">大正期</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="prop-footer">
        <div class="prop-tags"><span class="prop-tag prop-tag-area">長野県</span><span class="prop-tag prop-tag-type">古民家</span></div>
        <span class="prop-read-more">詳しく見る</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </a>
</div>
</Layout>
